message.content:
<REASONING> The task involves interacting with customers either over the phone or face-to-face. The primary responsibilities include providing information about the company's products or services, processing orders, handling account cancellations, and gathering details about customer complaints. This role requires effective communication skills, problem-solving abilities, and a customer-oriented approach to ensure customer satisfaction and address their needs effectively. </REASONING>

<OUTPUT_TEXT>
TASK – Confer with customers by telephone or in person to provide information about products or services, take or enter orders, cancel accounts, or obtain details of complaints.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
